  "text": "Previous studies like [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] focused on the represen-tation of the personality traits, and studied how users would disclose these visualized traits to others. However, in this study, our goal is about online self-presentation management. First, we want to investigate how people react to the results of personality traits of their own, not others, and secondly, we aim at providing clues to help users get insights on how their traits look like in certain way, rather than just presenting the computed levels of the traits [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
